net.trajano.doxdb.jdbc

Interface DoxDAO

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JdbcDoxDAO

    public interface DoxDAO
    This represents a single physical DoxDB table. There is going to be another one that manages all the other tables. The table creation responsibility would likely move over there.

    Applications are not meant to use this directly.
